 War II. He is most famous for having overseen the autopsy of  [[Adolf Hitler]] and Eva Braun in 1945.\n* 1946 : [[Isaac Trachtenberg]], member of [[National Academy of Sciences of Ukraine]]\n* [[Maryna Poroshenko]], [[First Lady of Ukraine]]\n* 1989 : [[Olga Bogomolets]], singer, songwriter, physician, and presidential candidate\n* [[Oleh Musiy]], [[Minister of Healthcare (Ukraine)]]\n\n<br />\n\n== Faculties and Department In Bogomolets National Medical University ==\n\n* Obstetrics and Gynecology<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.studynation360.com/bogomolets-national-medical-university-2-2/|title=Bogomolets National Medical University, Ukraine {{!}} Fees Structure 2020-2021|website=Study Nation 360|language=en-US|access-date=2020-03-12}}</ref>\n* Department of Internal Medicine\n* Surgery Department\n* Department of Infectious Diseases\n* Department of Neurology\n* Department of Neuro\u2013Surgery\n* Department of Radiology and Radiation Medicine\n* Department of Human Anatomy Morbid Physiology\n* Department Department of Pediatrics\n* Department of Forensic Medicine\n* Department of Traumatology and Orthopedics\n* Department of Internal Medicine\n* Department of Surgery \n\n== Bogomolets National Medical University Accreditation ==\n\n* World Health Organization (WHO)\n* Medical Council Of India (MCI) <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.studynation360.com/studymbbsinukraine/|title=MBBS in Ukraine - Fees Structure 2020, Duration, Eligibility, Reviews, NEET Requirement|website=Study Nation 360|language=en-US|access-date=2020-03-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.studynation360.com/mci-approved-mbbs-colleges-abroad/|title=List Of MCI Approved Medical Colleges Abroad 2020-2021 {{!}} MBBS Abroad 2020-21|website=Study Nation 360|language=en-US|access-date=2020-03-12}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Higher education in Kiev}}\n\n[[Category:Medical schools in Ukraine]]\n[[Category:Universities and colleges in Kiev]]\n[[Category:Bogomolets National Medical Un